data.title: Earth Hour unites people in Central and Eastern Europe
data.meta_description: With the official support of close to 300 cities across Austria, Hungary, Romania, Bulgaria, Serbia, Croatia and Ukraine, Earth Hour is becoming one of the biggest environmental events observed by thousands of people in Central and Eastern Europe.
